{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/lq6kfp","slide":10,"text":"This is the synthesis slide. Show that choices were intentional, not accidental.\nFor weaknesses, be direct: latency and app integration depth.\nClose with the main learning: the hard part is not just the LLM; it is the system around it: context, tools, feedback, memory, and reliability."}